---
import SectionHeader from '../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-24 bg-brand-softBg">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <SectionHeader
      title="A Team Built Around Course Systems"
    />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">

        <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm border border-brand-border/60 text-brand-primary">
               <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-lg mb-2">Course Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm">Curriculum planning and learner experience design.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm border border-brand-border/60 text-brand-primary">
               <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-lg mb-2">Content Conversion</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm">Transforming raw materials into learning assets.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm border border-brand-border/60 text-brand-primary">
               <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-lg mb-2">Platform Setup</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm">Kajabi, LMS configuration, and website building.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm border border-brand-border/60 text-brand-primary">
               <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-lg mb-2">Funnels & Automation</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm">Connecting marketing, checkout, and onboarding.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm border border-brand-border/60 text-brand-primary">
               <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-lg mb-2">AI-Assisted Workflows</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm">Speeding up production with human-reviewed AI.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-sm border border-brand-border/60 text-brand-primary">
               <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-lg mb-2">Ongoing Support</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-textMain text-sm">QA, maintenance, and post-launch improvements.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
